name: Plant_growth
description:
Seeing so much news about the little care of our planet, I believe that some humans, sometimes, in many places, are breaking down their own house.
I am starting a new series of works talking about the essence of natural wisdom.
I want to represent in some way, those natural parts that give us harmony to be able to stay in this place.
This piece represents the wisdom of caring for plants, both as small spaces at home as large areas in the world.

I hope this idea can awaken thought in your mind!

elio
